---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Dataset - Instrumetriq"
  description="Access the Instrumetriq sentiment dataset"
>
  <article>
    <h1>Dataset</h1>
    
    <section>
      <h2>About the Dataset</h2>
      <p>
        The Instrumetriq dataset contains sentiment data collected from various social media platforms.
        The dataset is designed for researchers and developers working on sentiment analysis,
        natural language processing, and social media studies.
      </p>
    </section>
    
    <section>
      <h2>Dataset Structure</h2>
      <p>
        Documentation about the dataset structure, format, and schema will be available once
        data collection reaches a stable milestone.
      </p>
    </section>
    
    <section>
      <h2>Access & Licensing</h2>
      <p>
        Information about dataset access, usage terms, and licensing will be provided here
        when the dataset is ready for distribution.
      </p>
    </section>
    
    <section>
      <h2>Citation</h2>
      <p>
        If you use this dataset in your research, please cite it appropriately. Citation
        guidelines will be provided with the dataset release.
      </p>
    </section>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  h1 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }
  
  section {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl);
  }
  
  h2 {
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }
</style>
